                      "model": "claude-sonnet-4-20250514",
                      "usage": {"input_tokens": 50, "output_tokens": 15}
                    }
                    """)));

        // WHY WIREMOCK:
        // 1. No real API call: free, fast, deterministic
        // 2. Test error scenarios: stub 503, timeout, malformed JSON
